articles.title: SJAA Officers
articles.summary: The document lists the current officers and board members for the San Jose Astronomical Association (SJAA). It identifies the President, Vice-president, Treasurer, and Secretary by name along with their phone numbers, and also names the organization's board members.

articles.title: RECENT ACTIVITIES:
articles.summary: This document details two recent astronomy club activities: an installation picnic and star party on July 13 at Levin Park, and a star party on July 20 at Henry Coe State Park. The Levin Park event had mixed success due to poor sky conditions, though a potential fireball was observed. In contrast, the Henry Coe State Park star party was highly successful, offering excellent viewing of various deep-sky objects and showcasing notable astronomical equipment.

articles.title: COMING EVENTS:
articles.summary: This article outlines upcoming astronomical events for August and September, featuring general meetings with discussions on topics like galaxies, an overnight star party coinciding with a new moon, and several public star parties. It also lists a board meeting and includes a request for bulletin submissions regarding future content.
